data.description: This home is as close to perfect as it gets. Completely redone in a modern style, bright and open. Very rare floorplan, each bedroom has its own full bathroom. Great set up for an airbnb. New 30 yr roof, new HVAC, updated plumbing, newer water heater,  3 new custom tile bath rooms, all new kitchen, new flooring and more. Large living room with high ceiling and woodburning fireplace. Large, open kitchen with all new cabinets, Quartz counters, new sink and plumbing fixtures, new stainless steel appliances. 5 burner gas stove. Main bedroom features a huge walk in shower with dual shower heads one is rainfall style. All baths have new vanities, fixtures and flooring.
